\v 5 K…ôni e nian r…ôfin ilah kautol t…®m…ôti. Inu noli…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm r…ôhalah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn t…ôrah, ilah k…ôut…ôluei e n…ôghati…ôn p…ôhri…ôn. Ilah, n…®kilah t…ôhti m…ôm…ô noli…ôn r…ôha n…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn e Uhg…®n in noli…ôn k…ôti o nosi…ôn m…ôni m…®ne naut…ô m…®n.\x - \xo 6:5 \xt 2Tim 3:8; 4:4; Tait 1:14\x*
